{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b5cdabe48","title":"对公安工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"526e912694","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"8b5cdabe48"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"cea9ce86b7","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8e9b0df89d","type":"paragraph","text":"八、依靠群众，加强专政，新疆办大型劳改农场不一定好，要研究；九、要抓学习，把工作做好，要精兵简政。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"96117d8b72","type":"paragraph","text":"对公安工作的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"b82a58bcb2","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月）","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"220c3fb299","type":"paragraph","text":"公安机关是无产阶级手里的一把刀子，掌握得好，就能打击敌人，保卫人民：掌握不好，就容易伤害自己。这把刀子要是被坏人抓走了，那就更加危险。所以，公安工作只能由党委直接领导，不能由业务部门垂直领导。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"48b9267de8","type":"paragraph","text":"关于陈毅的儿点指示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"634611759e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月十一日）（对北外造反团所编《陈裂黑斋集》的评语材料不黑，性情直爽。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"51050aa077","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"68bdf3f2c7","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"e0a24d7c61","type":"paragraph","text":"X陈毅是个好同志，对陈毅要一批二保。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"3d2de271c0","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"ccab2eba4b","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"1ece2726f0","type":"paragraph","text":"X要保他，他是第三野战军司命，外交部长现在汽人摘，还要他来搞。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"469747d3e0","type":"paragraph","text":"XX","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"072de866f3","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"c3eb6fd8ff","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅怎么能打倒呢？陈毅跟了我四十年，功芬么大。陈毅现在掉了二十斤内，不然我带他接见外宾。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"09726c0233","type":"paragraph","text":"对姚文元同志《陶焦的两本害》","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"57149c1836","type":"paragraph","text":"一文的批示","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"1a0b43d952","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年九月）好极！此文的要害是点破了“五·一六。”","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"50cdd4ba0f","type":"paragraph","text":"对新工作的指示","index":18,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"1f6b8c31ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年九月）新闻单位要树立严肃作风、科学作风、战斗作风，要培养无产阶级革命者的战斗风格。","index":19,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"290d408aad","type":"paragraph","text":"（据陈伯达同志1967年9月3日对新闻人员讲话时传达）","index":20,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"},{"id":"678f6e692d","type":"paragraph","text":"·325。","index":21,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48"}],"page":{"id":"bcea27c89b","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8b5cdabe48","start":338,"end":338}}}},"__N_SSG":true}